  <brief_title>Evaluation of a New Coating in Cement Less Femoral Stems</brief_title>
  <official_title>No Mid-term Advantage by Electrochemical Deposition of Hydroxyl-apatite in Cementless Femoral Stems. 5-year RSA and DXA Results From a Randomized Controlled Trial</official_title>
